name: History
description: The History class is a log of the significant events or actions performed by the involved parties during the course of handling the incident.

HistoryItem.name: HistoryItem
HistoryItem.description: An entry in the history log of significant events or actions performed by the involved parties.  See Section 3.13.1.

ext-restriction.name: ext-restriction
ext-restriction.description: A means by which to extend the restriction attribute.  See Section 5.1.1.
